title: Sydney Uni
body: Hi all Im in bronze 5 at sydney uni and looking for some new meta players on the campus. Preferably in bronze so we can think more alike! :) Message if interested

replies.body:
Recently escaped Bronze. Also at Camperdown/Darlington campus. Play all roles but have lately been maining jungle.
If you're interested, reply to this message.
heyyyyyyyyyy..............long time bronze 5 support main. im pretty interested :D:D    University of Sydney Camperdown/Darlington
Hai, I'm Bronze 3 and I main support and mid (: ~ Camperdown/Darlington campus

Hey! We have a club that deals with a bunch of games (starcraft, LoL, DotA, etc.) https://www.facebook.com/groups/suscogs/ . We'll have in house tournaments, lan parties, etc. Sign up and stay posted!
